Press raspberries through a fine wire-mesh strainer into a saucepan, discarding solids. Add water to raspberries. Combine SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener and cornstarch in a small bowl. Add to raspberry mixture, stirring until SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener dissolves. Cook over medium-high heat, stirring constantly, until mixture boils. Boil; stirring constantly for 1 minute. Cool. Cover and chill sauce 2 hours.